        </div>

        <p>After about 6 months, I was asked to reimagine the Action List tasks as part of our Digital Platform, instead of in an email. The Digital Platform is our custom patient portal that talks directly to our EHR platform (eClinicalWorks). It was created as part of our thoughtbot contract work <a class="anchor-body" href="/case-studies/groups" target="_blank">back in 2020</a>.  It was developed and designed by our team to serve as a more intuitive interface for staff to access the appointment data and medical records that live in our (clunky, difficult to navigate) EHR platform. Taking the Action List tasks out of a static email and into our Digital Platform meant they would become interactive and dynamic, and there would now be a sense of transparency and accountability among staff.</p>

