            <li>"AL helps me stay on task with what is needed to stay current so I don't have to remember everything I have to do!"</li>
            <li>"Everything makes me feel good about the work that I do!!"</li>
            <li>"AL can help me to stay organized and focused on the tasks that I need to complete."</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <p>As a designer, it makes me feel so good to make such a positive impact on our staff and members' lives, as well as on our business. Having a central place for task management in our Digital Platform means that we can now track task completion rate and size of workloads, to have better insight into how the work gets done and distributed to our staff. I'm looking forward to seeing how the Action List will change overtime, based on the insights we'll gain and feedback we'll continue to receive.</p>
